y":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"點解入禮頓？<br />\n巴閉囉，英雄主義，疊馬。<br />\n我唔妥你，我可以𢭃你；<br />\n我唔鍾意你，我可以𢱕你。<br />\n𡃁仔你睥咩呀？出嚟隻揪吖！<br />\n隻揪呀！<br />\n揪我吖！揪吖！<br />\n我揪你你揪我，點呀？"},{"pid":"4a7c2aca794a4acc05de7db7c4aa966d03a20103","tid":875742,"uid":32691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"061077d4274146dbe75fa846f9c4a3a05e0b88d1","tid":875742,"uid":55019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68670e8aeb6f5a99445394bf9989b37f548d36a2","tid":875742,"uid":32691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:30:49.000Z","msg":"助理管工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"19 AF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:47:47.000Z","msg":"明日動糧"},{"pid":"6a7fc94dabf01f5f85cc6b91d4e637d052e79dff","tid":875742,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765bc6a212496529bdadbeb32616662a8468cb70","tid":875742,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"做證人好大壓力，咁能多人望住你根本腦根一片空白。"},{"pid":"b3dba08e3b14668ecd1729acb03b42a76be3f4f6","tid":875742,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a7fc94dabf01f5f85cc6b91d4e637d052e79dff","tid":875742,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}